==Trivia==
* He is one of four [[NPCs]] to be seen wielding a [[two-handed sword]] with just one hand, the other three being [[Kamfreena]], [[Morgiana]], and [[Achtryn]].
* His combat level is no longer displayed when found outside of [[Tutorial Island]].
* According to [[Duradel]] in 20th [[Postbag from the Hedge]], Vannaka is a student of Duradel. He once challenged Duradel to a battle and lost.{{CitePostbag|issue=20|author=Duradel|letter=Letter 8|name=}}
* In ''[[RuneScape: Dragonwilds]]'', it is revealed that Vannaka is a [[werewolf]].

